{"tid":1564020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地輸緊囉！！！手足文宣即入[請廣傳]","createTime":"2019-09-12T15:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T15:47:17.000Z","uid":321381,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3d38f496b19c157bc718eacbafca3674c947ce88","tid":1564020,"uid":321381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:20:25.000Z","msg":"我知我系p牌仔，跪求大家睇完先！！！<br />\n<br />\n近依幾次大家出泥發夢<br />\n都有出火魔法同落地底挖礦掟野打魔龍<br />\n但系點解冇手足文宣<span style=\"color: orange;\">正名</span>or<span style=\"color: orange;\">解釋</span>or<span style=\"color: orange;\">道歉</span>返發生緊咩事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">依個一定要做</span></span><br />\n<br />\n701衝立法會第二日即刻有文宣解釋，812機場即刻有文宣道歉，咁灣仔嘅魔法路障呢?咁依兩日落地底挖礦呢?點解冇文宣解釋點泥?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">知唔知咁樣令好多淺黃比藍屍拉過去變藍</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地唔解釋就會比藍屍大做文章，淺黃好容易就變淺藍。<br />\n<br />\n我地做緊嘅系追求民主運動。<br />\n<br />\n我地系為香港以戰。我地做緊嘅野決定緊全香港人嘅未來。所以系咪應該要向香港人交待返發生咩事。<br />\n<br />\n冇錯就大大聲講我冇錯，做錯左就企定定系到比人dllm<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好以為佢會自己腦補，系就唔會系淺黃啦</span><br />\n<br />\n我見過牆紙講過火魔法，不過太多字，睇到我呢頭暈暈。有冇簡單易明嘅文宣解釋到，最後要講返邏輯因果關係。<br />\n<br />\n又話核彈都唔割，依家用下魔法，挖下礦，採下石就連文宣都冇。<br />\n<br />\n最後就系希望手足可以講返D唔系前線唔會知嘅事情比文宣知。<br />\n等D文宣巴絲可以幫你解釋。唔系都唔知點幫你。<br />\n<br />\n記住<br />\n我地卡關卡左正三個月<br />\n依家先過第一關<br />\n<br />\n後面只會一關比一關難<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人  再加油！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\nsor for 打打下變長文"},{"pid":"bf6f2ec4ce1eac636c09508cbe2808d011c26086","tid":1564020,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:20:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"85eb880b895a2e6d52dce1a0d2089811913f9d2b","tid":1564020,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:21:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e16431a12d356450727ec25e0b97a5fa2c2cca2c","tid":1564020,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:21:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgsafe.org/a5/a5c603334c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgsafe.org%2Fa5%2Fa5c603334c.jpeg&h=b13a8b01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8188a2ec0f9670add041ebaa28e06f65c885b2d6","tid":1564020,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:22:01.000Z","msg":"[文長][中期檢討]希望大家入黎睇下我地現有既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"f808e2c22a32547a4bfdfc4608aaab20526b6591","tid":1564020,"uid":321381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:23:42.000Z","msg":"自推十連<br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"334429ea79bc75b3e8986efe11a839dce99543ed","tid":1564020,"uid":321381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:23:56.000Z","msg":"自推十連<br />\n2/10"},{"pid":"d9018807191485cc60fda61ed4ee28bbb9108e21","tid":1564020,"uid":321381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:24:06.000Z","msg":"自推十連<br />\n3/10"},{"pid":"8fb5dbf71631c57cf13374fe4f27ec03f716b25a","tid":1564020,"uid":321381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0